OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FAfter two record-breaking heatwaves in
OL,7,Fas many months, it looks like July
OL,8,Fwill be heating up again next week.
OL,10,FBut this heatwave is expected to be
OL,11,Fquite different from the last, which
OL,12,Fsaw red weather warnings and health
OL,13,Falerts issued.
OL,15,FFrom its origin to how long it will
OL,16,Flast, and how uncomfortable it will
OL,17,Factually feel, here is how this
OL,18,Fheatwave is shaping up compared to the
OL,19,Flast.
OL,21,FWhen will the heat hit the UK?
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
