OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FAfter a much-needed, fresher feel the
OL,7,Flast few days - temperatures are set
OL,8,Fto rise again from the weekend onwards.
OL,10,FAnother high-pressure system,
OL,11,Fdescribed as some as "heat dome", will
OL,12,Fextend from the south west to bring
OL,13,Fsettled, dry and sunny conditions.
OL,15,FWhere is the heat coming from?
OL,17,FThis is not the same "heat dome" that
OL,18,Fbrought the extreme heatwave to the UK
OL,19,Fand parts of Europe last week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
