CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FThis system originates from a
OL,7,Fdifferent location - the Azores -
OL,8,Fwhich is in the south west of the UK
OL,9,Fin the North Atlantic Ocean.
OL,11,FMeteorologists give it the nickname
OL,12,Fthe "Azores High".
OL,14,FIt's a regular feature of our weather,
OL,15,Fand can be fortuitous in the summer
OL,16,Fmonths - as long as the jet stream
OL,17,Fisn't in the way.
OL,19,FHow hot will it be?
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
