CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FSome forecast data indicates
OL,7,Ftemperatures will lift again later in
OL,8,Fthe week to around 35C or more - but
OL,9,Fdetails will become clearer in the
OL,10,Fcoming days.
OL,12,FWill we be getting the uncomfortable
OL,13,Fhumidity we had in June
OL,15,FIt will feel muggy at times again with
OL,16,Fwarm and stuffy nights, but the
OL,17,Fhumidity will not be as noticeable as
OL,18,Flast week.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
