PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FSome of us will be in heatwave
OL,7,Fterritory again, just not quite the
OL,8,Foppressive widespread heat of last
OL,9,Fweek.
OL,11,FFor many, it will be manageable,
OL,12,Ftypical summer heat, and it has the
OL,13,Fpotential to last for nearly a week in
OL,14,Fplaces.
OL,16,FThe weekend after next has the
OL,17,Fpotential for thunderstorms to develop.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
