OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FParts of Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fwill feel fresher and cooler with
OL,8,Fbursts of rain at times, but where the
OL,9,Fsun shines will feel very pleasant,
OL,10,Fmore so to the east of high ground.
OL,12,FHow about the rest of summer?
OL,14,FAt a glance, there's a signal for high-
OL,15,Fpressure systems from the south to
OL,16,Fcome and go through the rest of the
OL,17,Fmonth.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
