PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782919121
OL,3,CHow will the next heatwave be
OL,4,Cdifferent from the last one?
OL,6,FRainfall is looking to be near
OL,7,Faverage, with regional variation of
OL,8,Fwetter or drier conditions - this is
OL,9,Fsteered by the hot weather generating
OL,10,Fthunderstorms.
